// 3. Sort columns in both grids - observe instant vs server-side behavior
// 4. Use text filter - observe warnings in left grid (partial mode)
// 5. Change maxCachedRows to 2000 - left grid should switch to full cache mode
// 6. Toggle indicators/warnings on/off to test visibility
